k":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-7yu","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":28106,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/23\/allah-has-waived-fasting-half-of-prayer\/","url_meta":{"origin":29046,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Travel: Allah has waived fasting, half of prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 23, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Amr ibn Umayyah reported: I came to the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, from a journey and he said, \u201cStay to eat, O Abu Umayyah.\u201d I said, \u201cIndeed, I am fasting.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cCome close to me and I will tell you about the traveler.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":23257,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/06\/20\/nothing-like-fasting\/","url_meta":{"origin":29046,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Fasting: Nothing is similar to fasting in reward","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 20, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Umamah reported: I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, tell me a deed to do.\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cYou must fast, for there is nothing equal to it.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304 2223 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0623\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0645\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15145,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/20\/angels-bless-fasting-feed-others\/","url_meta":{"origin":29046,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Fasting: Angels bless a fasting person who feeds others","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 20, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm 'Umarah bint Ka'b reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, entered her home and she served him food. The Prophet said, \u201cWill you eat?\u201d She said, \u201cIndeed, I am fasting.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cVerily, angels send blessings upon a fasting person when others eat in their presence\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":23320,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/06\/25\/fasting-fortress-shield-believers\/","url_meta":{"origin":29046,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Siyam: Fasting is a fortress, shield for believers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 25, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Umamah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cFasting is a shield and a fortress among the fortresses of the believer. Every deed is for its companion, but Allah says: Except fasting, as it is for Me, and I will reward it.\u201d Source: Musnad\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34162,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/04\/30\/do-not-insult-while-fasting\/","url_meta":{"origin":29046,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Siyam: Do not insult anyone while fasting","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 30, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cDo not insult anyone while you are fasting. If anyone insults you, then say: Indeed, I am fasting. If you are standing, then sit down.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn Khuzaymah 1994 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5253,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/17\/fasting-ramadan-six-days-shawwal\/","url_meta":{"origin":29046,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: Six more days of Shawwal like fasting a year","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 17, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Thawban reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cFasting the month of Ramadan is like ten months of fasting and fasting six days of Shawwal is like two months of fasting. Thus, they are like fasting for a year.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn Khuzaymah 2115 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/29046","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"hre